description: A person uses a grey pen to write "Hey Password '54321'" in black ink on a lined white paper with red margin lines. The person then tears the paper and crumples it into a small ball. A hand releases this crumpled white paper, allowing it to fall onto the floor next to a light-colored wall and a brown door.

children.description: A person uses a grey pen to write a message in black ink on a lined white paper with red margin lines. The message starts as "Hey Pass", is then updated to "Hey Password is "54321"", and finally written as "Hey Password '54321'". The person then tears the paper and crumples it into a small ball.
